        <h2>About Our System</h2>
        <p>
          The Facial Recognition Attendance System is an innovative approach to
          automate attendance management in a secure, efficient, and
          user-friendly way. It utilizes cutting-edge computer vision and
          machine learning technologies to recognize and verify individuals
          based on their facial features.
        </p>
        <p>
          This system is designed to replace traditional methods of attendance
          tracking, such as roll-calls or manual sign-ins, which can be
          time-consuming and prone to errors. With facial recognition
          technology, attendance can be marked with just a glance, significantly
          reducing the administrative workload and ensuring accurate
          record-keeping.
        </p>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>
          Our system uses a camera feed to capture real-time images of
          individuals and compares these images against a pre-registered
          database of students or employees. The software extracts facial
          features using machine learning models and matches them to identify
          individuals.
        </p>
        <p>
          The process is seamless, secure, and typically takes only a few
          seconds. Once an individual is identified, the system automatically
          logs the attendance in the database, providing instant updates for
          monitoring purposes.
        </p>
